---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Projects · InterStellar AI">
  <h1>Projects</h1>
  <p>
    Every project in the portfolio, with its stack and deploy target. Cross-referenced
    from the <a href="/decisions">decision log</a> for context on why the tech is what it
    is.
  </p>

  <h2>Reli</h2>
  <p>
    Personal AI assistant with a knowledge graph. Python/FastAPI + React, Postgres with
    pgvector. Deploy: <em>in transition</em> from self-hosted Tailscale/Docker to Railway
    staging + prod (see ADR-003).
  </p>

  <h2>Word Coach Annie</h2>
  <p>
    AI writing assistant for novelists. Next.js 15, PostgreSQL/Supabase, Prisma, MCP
    server with 48 tools. Deploy: Railway with staging → prod pipeline.
  </p>

  <h2>FilmDuel</h2>
  <p>
    Movie and TV ranking via ELO duels. FastAPI + React, PostgreSQL/Supabase. Deploy:
    Railway native auto-deploy — adding staging gate is tracked in filmduel issue #108.
  </p>

  <h2>Cosmic Match</h2>
  <p>
    Space-themed match-3 mobile game. Flutter + Flame. Ships as signed Android APK/AAB via
    GitHub Actions.
  </p>

  <h2>The Un-Reminder</h2>
  <p>
    Stochastic, context-aware habit prompts designed to defeat notification blindness.
    Native Android (Kotlin), on-device Gemma 4, no backend.
  </p>

  <h2>Archon</h2>
  <p>
    Open-source AI coding harness. YAML workflow engine that drives the automation
    pipeline every other project in this portfolio depends on.
  </p>

  <h2>Beads</h2>
  <p>
    Distributed graph issue tracker for AI agents. Go + Dolt.
  </p>
</Layout>
